          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/koduck/" class=" " title="怪怪物">怪怪物</a>
                (与时代脱节的凹凸曼)
              
                <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="31148282">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">从流浪乞讨、卖淫嫖娼而“三无人员”，从农民工而大学生，从“盲流”而“非法上访者”

谁能告诉我这个“从……而……”的行文是个什么来头？</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-04-06 15:52</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
